 38	 * Module brief:
 39	 * This module is used to add RRCRelease commands to the telnet server in the
 40	 * absence of full support for E2SM RAN Control (RC).
 41	 * This provides similar functionality to the ORAN.WG3.E2SM-RC-R003-v05.00 
 42	 * 8.4.5.4 RRC Connection Release Control which is initiated by the RIC. 
 43	 * 
 44	 * Implementation notes:
 45	 * We refer to the method call rrc_gNB_generate_RRCRelease at rrc_gNB_NGAP.c 
 46	 * during rrc_gNB_process_NGAP_UE_CONTEXT_RELEASE_COMMAND message generation. 
 47	 * 
 48	 * Building the telnetsrv and module:
 49	 * ./build_oai --build-lib telnetsrv
 50	 * 
 51	 * Loading the module:
